metadata.name: Marlena's Guetto
metadata.description:
Taking the inspiration with some Acid Jazz and having those sounds on the background is the essence of this track. 

We can hear those House rhythms always present and also that Marlena Shaw voice in front of you while that powerful bass is playing behind her. 

Imagine yourself having a drink next to the mediterranean beach, dancing in the sand with the people that you love.

By owning this NFT, you can contact Ruler B to get all the different channels individually.
